) that with the intention of creating love and affection between husband and wife recite YAA WADOO-DO 100 times on Friday and blow on any eatable and make them to eat, then there will too much love and affection between them.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a) se manqool hai keh miya biwi mein mohabbat o ulfat paiyda karne ki niyyat se Juma ke din kisi bhi khaane ki cheez par YAA WADOO-DO 100 martaba dam (blow) kar ke un dono ko khila di jaaye to un mein bohot ziyadah mohabbat o ulfat paiyda ho jaayegi.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ میاں بیوی میں محبت و اُلفت پیدا کرنے کی نیت سے جمعہ کے دن کسی بھی کھانے کی چیز پر ’’یَاوَدُودُ‘‘ 100 مرتبہ دم کر کے ان دونوں کو کھلادی جائے تو ان میں بہت زیادہ محبت و اُلفت پیدا ہوجائے گی۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": nul